name: Green Headgear
description: A woman of mystery, looking as if she just stepped out of the 1920s or maybe a 1930s supperclub. She is glamorous, beautiful, clad in headgear of various hues of green. You pause and look closer. Is she... Does her neck resemble the trunk of a majestic tree? If so, is her headgear less fashion and more like the top of a tree? A glamorous, gorgeous, alluring tree. It depends on what you see in this artwork. Imagination brings her into our brains and makes us want to know her story. What is her story?
